Do not think about anything else.

360
00:34:16,260 --> 00:34:18,080
Thank you, Sister Ruonan.

361
00:34:18,080 --> 00:34:22,670
Sister Ruonan, can you take me to see Miss?

362
00:34:22,670 --> 00:34:25,110
There are many people watching. Wait a bit longer.

363
00:34:25,110 --> 00:34:26,610
I will arrange for you to see Jin'er.

364
00:34:26,610 --> 00:34:30,860
All right! But it must be soon! Or else, I am afraid it will be too late.

365
00:34:30,860 --> 00:34:33,220
What do you mean "too late"?

366
00:34:33,220 --> 00:34:37,670
N-Nothing. It's just... a small matter.

367
00:34:37,670 --> 00:34:39,400
Well, I suppose it is not a small matter.

368
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:42,130
It is just a small personal...

369
00:34:43,470 --> 00:34:45,230
- private matter! <br> - What?

370
00:34:46,110 --> 00:34:49,800
- Private matter? <br> - Hurry back to your work! You must remember!

371
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:52,730
All right! Do not worry, I remember.

372
00:34:59,310 --> 00:35:02,210
Liu Qi insists that he was conspiring with you.

373
00:35:02,210 --> 00:35:05,120
Now, the entire city is covered in your wanted posters.

374
00:35:05,120 --> 00:35:08,430
His Majesty ordered to kill with no mercy.

375
00:35:08,430 --> 00:35:11,950
Older Brother, you were the one helping His Majesty uncover the rebels,

376
00:35:11,950 --> 00:35:14,420
yet this no longer makes sense.

377
00:35:14,420 --> 00:35:17,330
You and Sister-in-Law cannot stay here for long either.

378
00:35:17,330 --> 00:35:19,560
You should hurry and leave with Sister-in-Law.

379
00:35:19,560 --> 00:35:22,950
Go back to the border first. After all, that is the Chu family's territory.

380
00:35:22,950 --> 00:35:24,920
If that really doesn't work, then go to the Falcon Tribe.

381
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:28,130
After all, Princess Ma Ya and Yuan'er can definitely keep you both safe.

382
00:35:28,130 --> 00:35:30,190
It should not be like this.

383
00:35:30,190 --> 00:35:32,070
What shouldn't be like this?

384
00:35:33,390 --> 00:35:36,590
Because... taking Jin'er from prison

385
00:35:36,590 --> 00:35:39,290
was a deal between His Majesty and I.

386
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:50,980
<i>Your Majesty, I have guarded the border for over ten years.</i>

387
00:35:50,980 --> 00:35:53,300
<i>I gave it my all to resist the Falcon Tribe.</i>

388
00:35:53,300 --> 00:35:56,820
<i>Today, my wife committed a crime. You can punish me.</i>

389
00:35:56,820 --> 00:35:59,200
<i>Please spare my wife from suffering in prison.</i>

390
00:35:59,200 --> 00:36:03,170
<i>If you do not agree, I will not get up!</i>

391
00:36:03,170 --> 00:36:06,290
<i>You can save your wife if you want.</i>

392
00:36:08,950 --> 00:36:12,030
<i>But you must promise me one thing.</i>

393
00:36:14,030 --> 00:36:18,850
<i>Do you know that something major happened sixteen years ago?</i>

394
00:36:18,850 --> 00:36:23,490
<i>Sixteen years ago, I was still a child.</i>

395
00:36:24,370 --> 00:36:26,540
<i>How could I know about anything major that happened?</i>

396
00:36:26,540 --> 00:36:30,100
<i>Chu Xiuming, stop acting like you are clueless!</i>

397
00:36:31,010 --> 00:36:33,560
<i>Your wife, do you want to save her or not?</i>

398
00:36:33,560 --> 00:36:35,360
<i>I do!</i>

399
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,530
<i>All right.</i>

400
00:36:36,530 --> 00:36:38,880
<i>Please be frank with me.</i>

401
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:43,800
<i>Sixteen years ago, the Eighth Royal Manor was destroyed by a fire.</i>

402
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:46,530
<i>No one knows what injured Eighth Prince.</i>

403
00:36:46,530 --> 00:36:50,000
<i>His face was completely destroyed and his body ripped apart.</i>

404
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:52,450
<i>I have been continuously investigating this matter.</i>

405
00:36:52,450 --> 00:36:55,750
<i>Now, I have some evidence.</i>

406
00:36:55,750 --> 00:36:57,440
<i>What evidence?</i>

407
00:36:57,440 --> 00:37:02,380
<i>Back then, Eighth Prince was investigating the embezzlement of military funds.</i>

408
00:37:02,380 --> 00:37:06,200
<i>He mysteriously died before he found out who was behind it.</i>

409
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:11,320
<i> During these years, I have been investigating the matter according to Eighth Prince's clues. </i>

410
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:16,050
<i>The person behind it might already be aware.</i>

411
00:37:16,050 --> 00:37:20,600
<i>In order to keep this secret, he might wait for an opportunity to strike at me.</i>

412
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:25,320
<i>Right now, I want you to lure him out.</i>

413
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:27,400
<i>How?</i>

414
00:37:28,800 --> 00:37:31,770
<i> - By rebelling. <br> - Rebelling?!</i>

415
00:37:31,770 --> 00:37:37,780
<i>If you commit treason, then the mastermind is bound to pander to you and respond.</i>

416
00:37:42,600 --> 00:37:44,570
<i>- I... <br> - Do not worry!</i>

417
00:37:44,570 --> 00:37:48,250
<i>The entire Rui Royal Manor will be safe.</i>

418
00:37:56,830 --> 00:38:01,930
<i>Who do you think placed Xiuyuan into your family?</i>

419
00:38:18,830 --> 00:38:21,790
Then this does not make sense!

420
00:38:21,790 --> 00:38:24,310
Since this was an agreement between you and His Majesty

421
00:38:24,310 --> 00:38:26,470
and you already lured out the rebels,

422
00:38:26,470 --> 00:38:29,720
why does His Majesty still want to arrest you?

423
00:38:35,540 --> 00:38:38,090
That Liu Qi does not have that great of abilities

424
00:38:38,090 --> 00:38:41,300
to have harmed your entire family back then.

425
00:38:41,300 --> 00:38:44,090
Someone must be behind him.

426
00:38:44,090 --> 00:38:46,910
Now, no matter if it is for Jin'er's sake or mine,

427
00:38:46,910 --> 00:38:48,930
or for what happened back then,

428
00:38:48,930 --> 00:38:52,350
I must find that person behind all this.

429
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:56,140
Right now, Liu Qi is dead so we have nothing to go off of.

430
00:38:56,140 --> 00:38:59,500
How are we going to investigate? From where should we start?

431
00:39:03,620 --> 00:39:06,340
Uncle, you mentioned that rare object before.

432
00:39:06,340 --> 00:39:09,360
The gold orb that can change shape?

433
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:10,670
Yes.

434
00:39:10,670 --> 00:39:14,430
Uncle, where did you get that item from?

435
00:39:16,230 --> 00:39:20,410
My ninth brother, who is the current emperor, gave it to me.

436
00:39:20,410 --> 00:39:24,170
He said that someone gave it to him.

437
00:39:52,300 --> 00:39:55,210
Let's stop guessing.

438
00:39:55,210 --> 00:39:57,470
If we find the original owner of that rare object,

439
00:39:57,470 --> 00:40:00,580
then perhaps the truth will be revealed.

440
00:40:00,580 --> 00:40:04,780
But... it was so long ago, how do we investigate this?

441
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:12,060
Perhaps we can ask that elderly person.

442
