<i>[Situ Manor]</i>

443
00:40:44,420 --> 00:40:45,810
Who's there?

444
00:40:45,810 --> 00:40:47,550
Lord Situ.

445
00:40:50,020 --> 00:40:51,630
It is me.

446
00:40:51,630 --> 00:40:54,860
- Chu Xiuming? <br> - Greetings, My Lord.

447
00:40:54,860 --> 00:40:58,540
No—! You—! Aren't you a wanted criminal?

448
00:40:59,470 --> 00:41:00,840
I know.

449
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:03,310
You—! How could you come here?

450
00:41:03,310 --> 00:41:05,150
I need to ask for a favor.

451
00:41:05,150 --> 00:41:07,050
You still cannot come here!

452
00:41:07,050 --> 00:41:09,410
You— What am I supposed to do?

453
00:41:09,410 --> 00:41:12,730
My entire family can be killed for hiding you!

454
00:41:12,730 --> 00:41:15,820
If I captured you, how would I face my younger sister?

455
00:41:15,820 --> 00:41:17,930
Are you just putting me in a difficult position?

456
00:41:17,930 --> 00:41:20,870
Lord Situ, have you ever heard of a glass orb

457
00:41:20,870 --> 00:41:23,200
